OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrug baron jailed for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'terror tactics' arson     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fattack                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A notorious gangster who once tricked  
OL,6, the home secretary into early prison   
OL,7, release torched a #70,000 Range Rover  
OL,8, in a row over debt, a court was told.  
OL,10,FSheffield Crown Court heard Liverpool  
OL,11,Fcareer criminal John Haase committed   
OL,12,Fthe arson offence in March 2020 in     
OL,13,FSheffield while on licence from prison.
OL,15,FHaase, 74 and of HMP Frankland, was    
OL,16,Fsubsequently recalled to serve the     
OL,17,Fremainder of a 22-year prison sentence.
OL,19,FOn Thursday, he was jailed for nine    
OL,20,Fyears for the arson attack.            
